{"tid":1088601,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"痛恨利物浦  禾諾克: 對曼城努力避免輸10-11球","createTime":"2019-04-02T07:26:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-02T14:30:58.000Z","uid":62257,"like":35,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"959d5430564e1c7f5cc95a18c0aac4b4acf88c1f","tid":1088601,"uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T07:26:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://talksport.com/football/520428/neil-warnock-liverpool-premier-league-under-23s-man-city/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftalksport.com%2Ffootball%2F520428%2Fneil-warnock-liverpool-premier-league-under-23s-man-city%2F&d=mFE05qKCD2WHpL72sA8m60zlOXIvf7DEkQzrkg%2FJo1w%3D&h=f48046d4\" target=\"_blank\">https://talksport.com/football/520428/neil-warnock-liverpool-premier-league-under-23s-man-city/</a><br />\nWarnock blasted Premier League officials as &ldquo;the worst in the world&rdquo; and went on to suggest that he may field the kids against Man City ahead of next weekend&rsquo;s visit to relegation rivals Burnley,<br />\nHe said: &ldquo;We keep getting knock-backs. I will probably play the U23s on Wednesday against Manchester City and try to keep it down to 10 or 11.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/sports/禾諾克欲放水曼城真正原因係-132602871--spt.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.mobi.yahoo.com%2Fsports%2F%E7%A6%BE%E8%AB%BE%E5%85%8B%E6%AC%B2%E6%94%BE%E6%B0%B4%E6%9B%BC%E5%9F%8E%E7%9C%9F%E6%AD%A3%E5%8E%9F%E5%9B%A0%E4%BF%82-132602871--spt.html&d=mFE05qKCD2WHpL72sA8m60zlOXIvf7DEkQzrkg%2FJo1w%3D&h=1fc4f042\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/sports/禾諾克欲放水曼城真正原因係-132602871--spt.html</a><br />\n【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=mFE05qKCD2WHpL72sA8m60zlOXIvf7DEkQzrkg%2FJo1w%3D&h=b1d1d4cc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】周日卡迪夫城不敵車路士的英超大戰，主帥禾諾克對球證判決非常不滿，他表示會在周中對曼城的英超盡出後備球員以示威，但原來另有內情！<br />\n周日英超卡迪夫城對車路士，藍戰士右閘艾斯派古達處於越位位置入球，中堅魯迪格犯規亦沒有被逐，引起卡迪夫城主帥禾諾克（Neil Warnock）對球證非常不滿。<br />\n在賽後訪問中，禾諾克指雖然會努力在作客的環境中挑戰曼城，不會輸10球，但或會起用一些U23小將。這樣一來，曼城勢有更大勝算，打擊了跟他們正在爭逐冠軍的利物浦。<br />\n不過，禾諾克被翻舊賬，指他原來與利物浦素有積怨，因此放水曼城或是為了向紅軍復仇。<br />\n2011年，利物浦賽畢歐聯4強的賽事後，回到英超輪換9人，以0:1落敗予富咸，令到禾諾克當時執教的錫菲聯，因為對手得到重要3分而降班。當時他已經表示出對紅軍的怨恨，指自己會「記一世」。"},{"pid":"34a0b3ac503d5cf879c6178844198a1dd9d84a29","tid":1088601,"uid":2545,"like":3,"dislike":16,"score":-13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T07:28:30.000Z","msg":"Warnock=怨婦"},{"pid":"88d2e285c0ed7de1c5a76420da2291c18b44a445","tid":1088601,"uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T07:38:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e9afbe39e7132e82ed01d9168289351469e4e61","tid":1088601,"uid":40089,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T07:41:48.000Z","msg":"我地利記有神秘力量 怕你乜？"},{"pid":"2bd69608587083a9b6a8e96e16e45ecbd7d05880","tid":1088601,"uid":2419,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T07:48:03.000Z","msg":"講到唔放水曼城就會失分咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6bad493c5e03157c80b528e321a462fb07c1a3e","tid":1088601,"uid":22564,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T07:48:21.000Z","msg":"老老實實，出咩人都係比鏝炒架啦"},{"pid":"e4c14c3f6c682e6cb49dba21429d734f0c4038de","tid":1088601,"uid":88763,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T07:57:14.000Z","msg":"意思係話最多輸九粒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcede83c6b4fe51e320f2a277bf3e8d5a6129dbf","tid":1088601,"uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b6bad493c5e03157c80b528e321a462fb07c1a3e","tid":1088601,"uid":22564,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T07:48:21.000Z","msg